What you need to know:  The four were arrested in a private car by detectives from the Transnational and organized crimes unit (TOCU) After a tip-off via the Fichua Kwa DCI anonymous toll-free number, the Directorate of Criminal Investigations said.The four, Ali Mwakeo, Swaleh Mgoshi, Zacharia Mwakisuwa and Juma Mgosi, are in custody in Mombasa pending arraignment in court.